Banana Bran Muffins
Dry ingredients
1 cup all purpose flour
½ cup wheat bran
½ cup sugar (works best with Turbinado)
1 teaspoon baking powder
½ teaspoon baking soda
Pinch of salt

Wet ingredients
3 bananas mashed
⅓ cup butter melted
¼ cup milk
¼ cup honey
1 teaspoon vanilla

Options
⅓ cup currants
½ cup pecans
½ cup chocolate chips

Makes 18 standard sized muffins

Heat oven to 350F
Mix dry ingredients and options together
Mix wet ingredients
Add dry ingredients and options to the wet
Mix till just combined
Bake in 350F oven for 14-16 minutes (cake tester should come out clean, i like it when the sides are a little brown so i leave it in around 16 mins)


